# RoboLedger V5.2.25: Forensic Recon Hub & Metadata Intelligence

This update introduces the **Universal Reconciliation Hub**, providing real-time forensic balancing and high-fidelity metadata intelligence for both Asset and Liability ledgers.

## 🏛️ Universal Reconciliation Hub
A live, interactive calculator now resides on the right side of the **Switcher Bar**, perfectly aligned with the account pills.
- [x] **Dual-Mode Logic**:
    - **Asset Accounts (CHQ/SAV)**: `Opening - Total Debit + Total Credit = Ending`.
    - **Liability Accounts (VISA/MC/AMEX)**: `Opening + Total Debit - Total Credit = Ending`.
- [x] **Native Persistence**: Opening balances are editable directly in the bar and instantly saved to the forensic ledger.
- [x] **Horizontal Symmetry**: The UI is uniform and symmetrical, maintaining a professional "Wall Street" density.

## 💳 High-Fidelity CC Metadata
The ingestion engine now uses **IIN (Issuer Identification Number)** intelligence to classify and brand credit cards.
- [x] **Brand Detection**: Automatically identifies **VISA**, **Mastercard**, and **AMEX** based on the 15/16 digit numbering style.
- [x] **Advanced Branding**: Extracts bank-specific details to display branding like "**RBC AVION VISA**" or "**SCOTIABANK PASSPORT AMEX**".
- [x] **Dynamic Metadata**: The Action Bar now shows "**ALL LEDGERS**" in unified view, and full forensic tokens (Transit, Inst, ACC#) when a specific ledger is selected.

## 📐 Logic & Routing Hardening
- [x] **Ingestion Routing**: Fixed the bug where transactions uploaded from the "ALL" view were orphan-tagged. They now correctly resolve to the primary account ledger.
- [x] **Symmetrical UI**: Refined all horizontal utility strips to ensure a uniform, premium look across the island stack.

